README

Introduction
============
This project contains the source code used for the Audio Mixer used on the Dagomba Dance-Drumming site at Tufts University.

Example here:
https://wikis.uit.tufts.edu/confluence/display/DagombaDanceDrumming/Tora+Drum+Mixer

Usage:
======
           
<object classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" 
 id="audio_test" width="100%" height="640"
 codebase="http://fpdownload.macromedia.com/get/flashplayer/current/swflash.cab">

<param name="movie" value="/audio_mixer.swf" />
<param name="quality" value="high" />
<param name="bgcolor" value="#ffffff" />
<param name="allowScriptAccess" value="sameDomain" />
<param name="flashVars" value='trackTitle=Tora&track1File=ToraLeadLun.mp3&track1Name=LL&track2File=ToraAnsLun1.mp3&track2Name=AL1&track3File=ToraAnsLun2.mp3&track3Name=AL2&track4File=ToraGungon.mp3&track4Name=LGG&track5File=ToraGungon2.mp3&track5Name=LGG2' />

<embed src="/audio_mixer.swf" quality="high" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="100%" height="640" name="audio_test" align="middle" play="true" loop="false" quality="high" allowScriptAccess="sameDomain" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" pluginspage="http://www.adobe.com/go/getflashplayer" flashVars='trackTitle=Tora&track1File=ToraLeadLun.mp3&track1Name=LL&track2File=ToraAnsLun1.mp3&track2Name=AL1&track3File=ToraAnsLun2.mp3&track3Name=AL2&track4File=ToraGungon.mp3&track4Name=LGG&track5File=ToraGungon2.mp3&track5Name=LGG2'>
</embed>
</object>

Valid Parameters:
trackTitle - Display Title for overall track
track1File - filename of track
track1Name - Label for Track
track2File - filename of track
track2Name - Label for Track
track3File - filename of track
track3Name - Label for Track
track4File - filename of track
track4Name - Label for Track
track5File - filename of track
track5Name - Label for Track
